A market exchange where bitcoins can be bought and sold.

The only currency traded for bitcoins by this service is BRL (Brazilian Real).

Adding funds is performed through, MoIP (Money over IP) which transacts using the bank wire network.  Transactions are processed manually and may take 24 hours after to be processed.  Withdrawals occur through MoIP as well.

##History

The service was announced in July 13, 2011 (2.1).  The market did open to a limited trial later that month.

